            </a>
            
                <a href="/projects/anxs-postgresql.mirror/" title="Find out more about ANXS PostgreSQL" class="summary-inline">ANXS PostgreSQL is an Ansible role that simplifies the automated installation and configuration of PostgreSQL servers. It allows you to manage Postgres users, databases, extensions, and configuration parameters across environments. Built for infrastructure as code workflows, it helps DevOps teams maintain consistent Postgres setups.

</a>
            
