                <strong>Postgres Meta</strong>
            </a>
            
                <a href="/projects/postgres-meta.mirror/" title="Find out more about Postgres Meta" class="summary-inline">Postgres Meta is a RESTful API for managing PostgreSQL databases, developed by Supabase. It allows users to perform administrative tasks such as creating tables, views, functions, roles, and extensions programmatically through HTTP endpoints. Postgres Meta enables developers to integrate database management directly into dashboards, automation tools, or backend services without requiring SQL access or pgAdmin.

</a>
            
